        <briefdescription>
<para>This function sends IPI request to the target module and gets the response from it. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MailboxPtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to XMailbox </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MsgPtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to the payload message </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MsgLen</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Length of the message</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS If the IPI send and receive is successful</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE If there is a failure</para></listitem><listitem><para>Response received from server</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Payload consists of API ID and call arguments to be written in IPI buffer </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Send CDO to PLM through IPI. Return XST_FAILURE if sending data failed</para></listitem><listitem><para>Wait for IPI response from PLM with a timeout. If the timeout exceeds then error is returned otherwise it returns the status of the IPI response</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>        </inbodydescription>
